description: Dick party is probably the best name we can come up with, since there was plenty of dicks at this party. This latest submission has your typical dorm party, but everything changed once the game truth or dare showed up. There is something about that game that somehow it makes straight guys act totally gay, just for the sake of the dare. No exception in this party. First it was a harmless kiss, later getting caught in the bathroom making out and blowing your best friend, to going back in the room to find out your other friends already are getting it on like rabbits. A truly magical evening.
title: Dick Party
